## CSS Architecture

Three-layer cascade — choose the right layer, never mix them for the same property:

| Layer | Where | Use for |
|-------|-------|---------|
| 1. Base tokens | `globals.css :root` | Warm neutral defaults (shipped baseline) |
| 2. Client theme class | `globals.css .theme-{client}` | Static per-client overrides applied at build time |
| 3. Runtime tokens | `<ThemeProvider tokens={…}>` | Dynamic JS-driven overrides |

Apply a client theme: add `.theme-qantas` to `<body>` or a wrapper `<div>`.
Dark mode: add `.dark` to a parent element, or pass `dark` prop to `ThemeProvider`.

### Theme Tokens
```typescript
// Colors
bg-background, text-foreground, bg-card, text-card-foreground
bg-primary, text-primary-foreground, bg-secondary, text-secondary-foreground
bg-muted, text-muted-foreground, bg-accent, text-accent-foreground
bg-destructive, text-destructive-foreground, border-border, ring-ring

// Icons (≤48px: standard weight, >48px: thin stroke)
import { ICON_STROKE_WIDTH } from "@/lib/theme-config"  // → 1.5
<Info size={24} />                                       // ≤48px: no override needed
<Heart size={64} strokeWidth={ICON_STROKE_WIDTH} />      // >48px: thin
```

### White-Label Quick Setup

Minimum overrides for a brand identity — everything else inherits from the baseline:

```css
.theme-myclient {
  --primary: oklch(…);             /* Brand colour — buttons, CTAs, links */
  --primary-foreground: oklch(…);  /* Text on primary (usually white) */
  --radius: 0.5rem;                /* 0 = sharp edges · 0.5rem = clean · 1.5rem = pill */
  /* Optional: */
  --background: oklch(…);
  --foreground: oklch(…);
}
```

Industry starting points:
- **Travel / Airlines** — `--primary: oklch(0.42 0.16 245)` — sky blue · `--radius: 0.5rem`
- **Retail / Grocery** — `--primary: oklch(0.55 0.22 27)` — warm red · `--radius: 0.375rem`
- **Healthcare** — `--primary: oklch(0.52 0.12 196)` — calm teal · `--radius: 0.625rem`
- **Finance / Insurance** — `--primary: oklch(0.27 0.09 243)` — navy (baseline default)
- **Pharmacy** — `--primary: oklch(0.45 0.18 260)` — blue-violet · `--radius: 0.25rem`

