## Component Creation Checklist

### Before Writing Code
- [ ] Search existing components (grep/glob)
- [ ] New tokens needed? **NOTIFY USER** — don't create without approval
- [ ] Identify atom / molecule / organism

### During Creation
- [ ] Use shadcn/ui `Button` — never raw `<button>`
- [ ] Theme tokens only — no hex, rgb, hardcoded colors
- [ ] Icons: ≤48px standard · >48px use `ICON_STROKE_WIDTH`
- [ ] Responsive: `h-12 md:h-10` on every interactive element, progressive spacing at every breakpoint
- [ ] a11y: `aria-label`, `alt`, `aria-live` regions
- [ ] If the component animates or transitions — **also invoke `#motion`**

### Post-Creation
- [ ] Test light + dark mode
- [ ] Test mobile → tablet → desktop
- [ ] No hardcoded values anywhere

