## Common Mistakes

**❌ DON'T:**
- Raw `<button>` — always use shadcn `<Button>`
- Paste Figma values directly (`#2563EB`, `bg-[#2563EB]`)
- Hardcode colors, spacing, or stroke widths
- Skip `md:` variants — every component must scale
- Big breakpoint jumps (`px-4 lg:px-32`)
- Build for desktop first, then try to shrink to mobile
- `style={{ width: X, height: X }}` for dimensions — inline styles bypass Tailwind's responsive system entirely. Use `size-*`, `w-*`, `h-*` classes so `md:` variants remain available
- `text-[18px]`, `text-[25px]` without an `md:` pair — use the typography table above or approve the exception explicitly (constrained native-style components only)

**✅ DO:**
- Search repo before creating anything new
- Progressive spacing: `p-4 md:p-6 lg:p-8`
- Touch targets: `h-12 md:h-10` on all interactive elements
- Use `100dvh` (not `100vh`) for full-screen mobile layouts
- `ICON_STROKE_WIDTH` for icons >48px

